      "content": "have u ever looked closely at those specific blue and grey plaid patterns they sell at places like gap or h&m? i was looking at one today and it felt... weirdly hypnotic. like it's designed to make u just tune out and not think too hard. is there actually any science to how patterns affect mood or compliance?",
